title: ARETE: The Heart of 100-0, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO222
itunes:title: ARETE: The Heart of 100-0, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO222
description: What do all these things have in common? “In God We Trust.” An Eagle. The Greek heroes Achilles and Odysseus. The Roman hero Aeneas. Wealth. Excellence. Impact. Legacy. The MFCEO Project. 100-0....and YOU. In this episode, I answer that question, identify the driving force behind the 100-0 movement, explain what's at stake, and issue a challenge. Listen like your life depended on it...because it does.
